## P0 (Must-have for v0.5.1)

### 1. Network Policy Enforcement
- ~~Document which services must bind 127.0.0.1 vs 0.0.0.0~~ ✅ **Completed in v0.5.0**
- ~~Add IPDeny=any to all non-exposed services~~ ⚠️ **Reverted due to systemd compatibility issues**
- Audit aitbc-marketplace.service and aitbc-exchange.service for exposure requirements
- Apply alternative network hardening (firewall rules, port binding restrictions)
- **Note**: IPDeny=any causes systemd compatibility issues; use firewall rules instead

### 2. Secret Rotation Dry-Run
- ~~Execute the rotation runbook (docs/operations/SECRETS.md)~~ ✅ **Runbook completed in v0.5.0**
