- ~~Flaky-test detection: Add pytest --reruns 2~~ ✅ **Completed in v0.5.0**
- ~~Separate lint and test jobs~~ ✅ **Completed in v0.5.0**
- Validate CI/CD changes work correctly in production
- Monitor flaky test rerun counts as CI metric

